{"id": "work_a15f6813-bfc4-5878-962f-a72c1ae355cd", "title": "Dataset Security for Machine Learning: Data Poisoning, Backdoor Attacks, and Defenses", "sources": [{"source": "dtic", "id": "pub.1146568087"}], "last_updated": "2026-03-09T19:37:26.239874", "abstract": "As machine learning systems grow in scale, so do their training data requirements, forcing practitioners to automate and outsource the curation of training data in order to achieve state-of-the-art performance. The absence of trustworthy human supervision over the data collection process exposes organizations to security vulnerabilities; training data can be manipulated to control and degrade the downstream behaviors of learned models. The goal of this work is to systematically categorize and discuss a wide range of dataset vulnerabilities and exploits, approaches for defending against these threats, and an array of open problems in this space.", "publication_date": "2023-01-06", "doi": "10.1109/tpami.2022.3162397", "url": "https://dtic.dimensions.ai/details/publication/pub.1146568087?and_facet_researcher=ur.012401467325.50", "citation_count": 0, "authors": [{"author_id": "author_2774b6a5-1cd5-5c35-ba7b-d0f11d50f5ca", "org_id": "org_9dac9558-93cb-59a1-8f5c-15af8f7be910"}, {"author_id": "author_79e2bf38-5eb2-5c41-835c-454497ebe7f1", "org_id": "org_4b380dd8-ef65-5307-8649-24e87928f6c0"}, {"author_id": "author_cc4ca0dd-ab5a-50db-b6dc-2a099ab67abd", "org_id": "org_9e6ac9b2-55fd-5d9f-9f3d-ec4c1d396558"}, {"author_id": "author_b6eb9784-b7e8-50a5-9b0d-1787e8d872af", "org_id": "org_6c5fd98f-0767-506e-8834-dbe4e6d6ac09"}, {"author_id": "author_d947fe27-475b-568f-9ac8-57b8e2fc1f19", "org_id": "org_9dac9558-93cb-59a1-8f5c-15af8f7be910"}, {"author_id": "author_e4f78dc2-037a-55fe-af58-76394a7771da", "org_id": "org_6c5fd98f-0767-506e-8834-dbe4e6d6ac09"}, {"author_id": "author_e22591aa-c117-5789-be67-c5819c179535", "org_id": "org_4b380dd8-ef65-5307-8649-24e87928f6c0"}, {"author_id": "author_24259b4f-7e97-5b9b-b514-595533babfe1", "org_id": "org_9e6ac9b2-55fd-5d9f-9f3d-ec4c1d396558"}, {"author_id": "author_ea27e7fa-752f-56ba-9767-9b53e37ec565", "org_id": "org_9dac9558-93cb-59a1-8f5c-15af8f7be910"}], "orgs": [{"org_id": "org_9dac9558-93cb-59a1-8f5c-15af8f7be910", "role": "affiliation"}, {"org_id": "org_4b380dd8-ef65-5307-8649-24e87928f6c0", "role": "affiliation"}, {"org_id": "org_9e6ac9b2-55fd-5d9f-9f3d-ec4c1d396558", "role": "affiliation"}, {"org_id": "org_6c5fd98f-0767-506e-8834-dbe4e6d6ac09", "role": "affiliation"}], "topics": [{"topic_id": "topic_14fcb8f7-9bc4-5fa9-ac84-fa42a73b2898", "score": 1.0}, {"topic_id": "topic_b92e3636-64b9-5642-b37d-5b2fc99a4718", "score": 1.0}, {"topic_id": "topic_0187738f-8e44-5d82-a948-7a6c2b6dd68f", "score": 1.0}], "created_at": "2026-03-09T19:37:26.239874"}